### ================================================================
### Smart Parking — Executive Summary API Tests
### ================================================================
### Run with: VS Code REST Client / Thunder Client / curl
### Ensure backend is running: cd backend && node index.js
### ================================================================

@base = http://localhost:8000/api
@contentType = application/json

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1a. GET /api/analytics/executive-summary — Full summary
GET {{base}}/analytics/executive-summary

### Expected: 200
### {
###   "success": true,
###   "generated_at": "...",
###   "system_status": "healthy|moderate|warning|critical",
###   "health_score": 0-100,
###   "data": {
###     "occupancy": { ... },
###     "predictions": { ... },
###     "violations": { ... },
###     "recommendations": [ ... ]
###   },
###   "metadata": { ... }
### }


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. INDIVIDUAL ANALYTICS ENDPOINTS (for comparison)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2a. GET /api/analytics/efficiency/slots — Live slot efficiency
GET {{base}}/analytics/efficiency/slots

### 2b. GET /api/analytics/occupancy/trends — Occupancy trends
GET {{base}}/analytics/occupancy/trends?range=1d

### 2c. GET /api/analytics/bottlenecks — Bottleneck detection
GET {{base}}/analytics/bottlenecks

### 2d. GET /api/analytics/violation/hotspots — Violation hotspots
GET {{base}}/analytics/violation/hotspots?limit=5

### 2e. GET /api/analytics/efficiency — System efficiency
GET {{base}}/analytics/efficiency
